<dashboard version="1.1" theme="dark">
  <label>📖 Panduan Gemini SOC Assistant V2.0</label>
  <description>Dokumentasi lengkap perintah | geminianalyze — analisis log berbasis AI untuk tim SOC.</description>

  <row>
    <panel>
      <html>
        <div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f2027,#203a43,#2c5364);color:#fff;padding:28px 32px;border-radius:10px;box-shadow:0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);">
          <h1 style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:1.8em;">🛡️ Gemini SOC Assistant — V2.0</h1>
          <p style="margin:0;font-size:1.05em;line-height:1.7;color:#b0d4e8;">
            Asisten AI untuk tim SOC berbasis Splunk. Didukung oleh <b>Gemma 4</b> dan <b>Gemini</b>,
            dirancang untuk menghasilkan analisis log yang <b>detail, komprehensif, dan langsung actionable</b>
            — tanpa noise, tanpa basa-basi, tanpa mengulang prompt.
          </p>
          <div style="margin-top:16px;display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap;">
            <span style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);padding:5px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:0.85em;">✅ Anti-Echo Output</span>
            <span style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);padding:5px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:0.85em;">✅ Native System Instruction</span>
            <span style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);padding:5px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:0.85em;">✅ 5 Role Bawaan</span>
            <span style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);padding:5px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:0.85em;">✅ MITRE ATT&amp;CK Mapping</span>
            <span style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);padding:5px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:0.85em;">✅ Batch Mode</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>

  <row>
    <panel>
      <title>🆕 Yang Berubah di V2</title>
      <html>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;">
          <div style="padding:16px;border-left:4px solid #00b4d8;background:#1a2a35;border-radius:6px;">
            <h4 style="color:#00b4d8;margin:0 0 8px 0;">🧠 Prompt Engine Baru</h4>
            <p style="color:#ccc;margin:0;font-size:0.92em;">Menggunakan <code>system_instruction</code> field native Gemini API sehingga aturan AI benar-benar terpisah dari data pengguna. Hasilnya: AI lebih patuh dan output jauh lebih bersih.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:16px;border-left:4px solid #06d6a0;background:#1a2a35;border-radius:6px;">
            <h4 style="color:#06d6a0;margin:0 0 8px 0;">🚫 Anti-Echo &amp; Anti-Noise</h4>
            <p style="color:#ccc;margin:0;font-size:0.92em;">Output cleaner pipeline berlapis: buang tag bocor, buang echo prompt, buang kata pengantar. AI langsung mulai dengan TEMUAN, bukan "Berikut adalah analisis saya...".</p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:16px;border-left:4px solid #ffd166;background:#1a2a35;border-radius:6px;">
            <h4 style="color:#ffd166;margin:0 0 8px 0;">📏 Analisis Lebih Panjang</h4>
            <p style="color:#ccc;margin:0;font-size:0.92em;"><code>maxOutputTokens: 4096</code> — analisis tidak akan terpotong di tengah. Temperature 0.4 membuat output lebih ekspansif dan kaya detail tanpa kehilangan akurasi.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:16px;border-left:4px solid #ef476f;background:#1a2a35;border-radius:6px;">
            <h4 style="color:#ef476f;margin:0 0 8px 0;">🎭 5 Role Specialist Baru</h4>
            <p style="color:#ccc;margin:0;font-size:0.92em;">Ditambahkan role <code>threat_hunter</code>, <code>malware_analyst</code>, dan <code>executive_report</code> dengan template output Markdown terstruktur + MITRE ATT&amp;CK mapping.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>

  <row>
    <panel>
      <title>📋 Parameter Perintah | geminianalyze</title>
      <html>
        <table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-family:sans-serif;">
          <tr style="background:#006d9c;color:#fff;">
            <th style="padding:11px 14px;border:1px solid #444;text-align:left;">Parameter</th>
            <th style="padding:11px 14px;border:1px solid #444;text-align:left;">Wajib?</th>
            <th style="padding:11px 14px;border:1px solid #444;text-align:left;">Default</th>
            <th style="padding:11px 14px;border:1px solid #444;text-align:left;">Keterangan</th>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background:#1e2b33;">
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#7ec8e3;"><b>prompt</b></td>
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#06d6a0;">✅ Ya</td>
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#aaa;">—</td>
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#ddd;">Instruksi tugas untuk AI. Tulis senatural mungkin. Contoh: <code>"Identifikasi teknik brute force dan rekomendasikan mitigasi."</code></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background:#16212a;">
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#7ec8e3;"><b>role</b></td>
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#aaa;">❌ Tidak</td>
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#aaa;"><code>soc_clean_report</code></td>
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#ddd;">Persona AI. Pilih: <code>soc_clean_report</code> | <code>threat_hunter</code> | <code>malware_analyst</code> | <code>executive_report</code> | <code>json_extractor</code></td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background:#1e2b33;">
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#7ec8e3;"><b>batch</b></td>
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#aaa;">❌ Tidak</td>
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#aaa;"><code>false</code></td>
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#ddd;"><code>false</code> = analisis per baris log (baik untuk investigasi detail). <code>true</code> = semua log digabung jadi 1 analisis besar (baik untuk rangkuman insiden).</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background:#16212a;">
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#7ec8e3;"><b>field</b></td>
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#aaa;">❌ Tidak</td>
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#aaa;"><code>_raw</code></td>
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#ddd;">Field yang dikirim ke AI. Jika field tidak ada, otomatis mengambil seluruh record sebagai JSON.</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background:#1e2b33;">
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#7ec8e3;"><b>model</b></td>
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#aaa;">❌ Tidak</td>
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#aaa;">(dari Setup)</td>
            <td style="padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #444;color:#ddd;">Override model on-the-fly. Contoh: <code>model="gemini-3.1-pro"</code>. Berguna untuk investigasi berat yang butuh model Pro.</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <p style="color:#aaa;margin-top:10px;font-size:0.9em;">💡 <b>Field output baru di V2:</b> <code>gemini_analysis</code>, <code>gemini_analysis_length</code>, <code>gemini_task_sent</code>, <code>analysis_mode</code>, <code>ai_model</code>, <code>ai_role</code>, <code>record_count</code> (batch only)</p>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>

  <row>
    <panel>
      <title>🎭 Katalog Role Bawaan</title>
      <html>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;">
          <div style="padding:14px;border:1px solid #2a4a5a;border-radius:7px;background:#16212a;">
            <h4 style="color:#00b4d8;margin:0 0 6px 0;"><code>soc_clean_report</code> (Default)</h4>
            <p style="color:#ccc;margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:0.9em;">Laporan insiden terstruktur: Detail Teknis, Penilaian Ancaman, Rekomendasi. Terbaik untuk investigasi harian SOC.</p>
            <code style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.8em;">role="soc_clean_report"</code>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:14px;border:1px solid #2a4a5a;border-radius:7px;background:#16212a;">
            <h4 style="color:#ef476f;margin:0 0 6px 0;"><code>threat_hunter</code></h4>
            <p style="color:#ccc;margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:0.9em;">IOC table, MITRE ATT&amp;CK mapping, kill chain reconstruction, dan query hunting lanjutan.</p>
            <code style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.8em;">role="threat_hunter"</code>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:14px;border:1px solid #2a4a5a;border-radius:7px;background:#16212a;">
            <h4 style="color:#ffd166;margin:0 0 6px 0;"><code>malware_analyst</code></h4>
            <p style="color:#ccc;margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:0.9em;">Klasifikasi malware, kapabilitas teknis (C2, persistence, evasion), skor risiko, dan rule deteksi.</p>
            <code style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.8em;">role="malware_analyst"</code>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:14px;border:1px solid #2a4a5a;border-radius:7px;background:#16212a;">
            <h4 style="color:#06d6a0;margin:0 0 6px 0;"><code>executive_report</code></h4>
            <p style="color:#ccc;margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:0.9em;">Laporan level CISO/Direksi: non-teknis, fokus dampak bisnis, risiko regulasi (UU PDP), rekomendasi strategis.</p>
            <code style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.8em;">role="executive_report"</code>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:14px;border:1px solid #2a4a5a;border-radius:7px;background:#16212a;">
            <h4 style="color:#c77dff;margin:0 0 6px 0;"><code>json_extractor</code></h4>
            <p style="color:#ccc;margin:0 0 6px 0;font-size:0.9em;">Output STRICT JSON only — untuk integrasi SOAR, enrichment pipeline, atau automation. Tidak ada teks Markdown.</p>
            <code style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.8em;">role="json_extractor"</code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>

  <row>
    <panel>
      <title>🧪 Contoh Query Interaktif (Klik untuk membuka)</title>
      <html>
        <div style="background:#1a2332;padding:20px;border-radius:8px;">

          <details style="margin-bottom:12px;background:#0d1b22;border:1px solid #2a4a5a;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;">
            <summary style="padding:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#00b4d8;font-size:1.1em;outline:none;">1. Investigasi Brute Force (Single)</summary>
            <div style="padding:0 14px 14px 14px;">
              <p style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.9em;margin:0 0 8px 0;">Analisis mendalam per baris log gagal login.</p>
              <pre style="background:#000;color:#0f0;padding:12px;border-radius:5px;font-size:0.85em;white-space:pre-wrap;border-left:3px solid #00b4d8;">index=wineventlog EventCode=4625
| head 10
| geminianalyze prompt="Identifikasi apakah ini brute force, password spray, atau credential stuffing. Sertakan teknik MITRE ATT&amp;CK yang relevan."</pre>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details style="margin-bottom:12px;background:#0d1b22;border:1px solid #2a4a5a;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;">
            <summary style="padding:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#ef476f;font-size:1.1em;outline:none;">2. Ringkasan Insiden Massal (Batch Mode)</summary>
            <div style="padding:0 14px 14px 14px;">
              <p style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.9em;margin:0 0 8px 0;">Gabungkan ratusan log menjadi satu analisis komprehensif.</p>
              <pre style="background:#000;color:#0f0;padding:12px;border-radius:5px;font-size:0.85em;white-space:pre-wrap;border-left:3px solid #ef476f;">index=firewall action=blocked
| head 100
| geminianalyze prompt="Identifikasi pola serangan, IP paling agresif, dan port yang paling ditarget." batch=true role="threat_hunter"</pre>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details style="margin-bottom:12px;background:#0d1b22;border:1px solid #2a4a5a;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;">
            <summary style="padding:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#ffd166;font-size:1.1em;outline:none;">3. Analisis Tabel Stats (Auto-JSON)</summary>
            <div style="padding:0 14px 14px 14px;">
              <p style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.9em;margin:0 0 8px 0;">AI membaca data tabel agregat meskipun tidak ada _raw.</p>
              <pre style="background:#000;color:#0f0;padding:12px;border-radius:5px;font-size:0.85em;white-space:pre-wrap;border-left:3px solid #ffd166;">index=main
| stats count by src_ip, dest_port, action
| sort -count
| head 20
| geminianalyze prompt="Analisis IP mana yang paling berbahaya dan apakah ada indikasi port scanning atau C2 communication."</pre>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details style="margin-bottom:12px;background:#0d1b22;border:1px solid #2a4a5a;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;">
            <summary style="padding:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#06d6a0;font-size:1.1em;outline:none;">4. Laporan Eksekutif</summary>
            <div style="padding:0 14px 14px 14px;">
              <p style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.9em;margin:0 0 8px 0;">Laporan non-teknis siap untuk manajemen/CISO.</p>
              <pre style="background:#000;color:#0f0;padding:12px;border-radius:5px;font-size:0.85em;white-space:pre-wrap;border-left:3px solid #06d6a0;">index=main tag=incident
| head 1
| geminianalyze prompt="Buatkan laporan insiden untuk Dewan Direksi." role="executive_report"</pre>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details style="margin-bottom:12px;background:#0d1b22;border:1px solid #2a4a5a;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;">
            <summary style="padding:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#c77dff;font-size:1.1em;outline:none;">5. Ekstraksi IOC untuk SOAR</summary>
            <div style="padding:0 14px 14px 14px;">
              <p style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.9em;margin:0 0 8px 0;">Output JSON murni siap dikonsumsi oleh automation pipeline.</p>
              <pre style="background:#000;color:#0f0;padding:12px;border-radius:5px;font-size:0.85em;white-space:pre-wrap;border-left:3px solid #c77dff;">index=proxy
| head 20
| geminianalyze prompt="Ekstrak semua IOC dari log ini." role="json_extractor"
| table _time, gemini_analysis</pre>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details style="background:#0d1b22;border:1px solid #2a4a5a;border-radius:6px;cursor:pointer;">
            <summary style="padding:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#ff9f43;font-size:1.1em;outline:none;">6. Deep Forensics (Override Model Pro)</summary>
            <div style="padding:0 14px 14px 14px;">
              <p style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.9em;margin:0 0 8px 0;">Gunakan model paling canggih untuk kasus kompleks.</p>
              <pre style="background:#000;color:#0f0;padding:12px;border-radius:5px;font-size:0.85em;white-space:pre-wrap;border-left:3px solid #ff9f43;">| makeresults
| eval _raw="[payload berbahaya Anda di sini]"
| geminianalyze prompt="Lakukan bedah forensik menyeluruh pada payload ini." role="malware_analyst" model="gemini-3.1-pro"</pre>
            </div>
          </details>

        </div>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>

  <row>
    <panel>
      <title>⚙️ Alur Kerja Optimal V2</title>
      <html>
        <div style="display:flex;gap:0;align-items:stretch;flex-wrap:wrap;">
          <div style="flex:1;min-width:160px;padding:18px;background:#0f2c1e;border-left:4px solid #06d6a0;margin:4px;">
            <div style="font-size:1.8em;margin-bottom:6px;">①</div>
            <b style="color:#06d6a0;">Ambil Data</b>
            <p style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.88em;margin:8px 0 0 0;">Gunakan SPL standar. Semakin spesifik filter Anda, semakin relevan analisis AI.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="flex:1;min-width:160px;padding:18px;background:#0f1f2c;border-left:4px solid #00b4d8;margin:4px;">
            <div style="font-size:1.8em;margin-bottom:6px;">②</div>
            <b style="color:#00b4d8;">Pilih Mode</b>
            <p style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.88em;margin:8px 0 0 0;">Per-baris (<code>batch=false</code>) untuk investigasi individual. Batch (<code>batch=true</code>) untuk rangkuman.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="flex:1;min-width:160px;padding:18px;background:#1f1a2e;border-left:4px solid #c77dff;margin:4px;">
            <div style="font-size:1.8em;margin-bottom:6px;">③</div>
            <b style="color:#c77dff;">Pilih Role</b>
            <p style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.88em;margin:8px 0 0 0;">Sesuaikan role dengan audiens: SOC analyst, threat hunter, atau eksekutif.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="flex:1;min-width:160px;padding:18px;background:#2c1f0f;border-left:4px solid #ffd166;margin:4px;">
            <div style="font-size:1.8em;margin-bottom:6px;">④</div>
            <b style="color:#ffd166;">Tulis Prompt</b>
            <p style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.88em;margin:8px 0 0 0;">Tulis pertanyaan investigasi Anda. Semakin spesifik prompt, semakin dalam analisis AI.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="flex:1;min-width:160px;padding:18px;background:#2c0f14;border-left:4px solid #ef476f;margin:4px;">
            <div style="font-size:1.8em;margin-bottom:6px;">⑤</div>
            <b style="color:#ef476f;">Tampilkan Hasil</b>
            <p style="color:#aaa;font-size:0.88em;margin:8px 0 0 0;">Gunakan <code>| table gemini_analysis</code> atau masukkan ke dashboard laporan SOC Anda.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top:16px;padding:14px;background:#1a2a1a;border-left:5px solid #06d6a0;border-radius:4px;">
          <b style="color:#06d6a0;">💡 Tips Ahli V2:</b>
          <span style="color:#ccc;"> Untuk monitoring kualitas, tambahkan <code>| table gemini_analysis, gemini_analysis_length, ai_model, ai_role</code>.
          Field <code>gemini_analysis_length</code> membantu Anda memantau apakah AI memberikan output yang cukup detail (idealnya &gt; 500 karakter per analisis).</span>
        </div>
      </html>
    </panel>
  </row>

</dashboard>